Admittance: The teacher wrote about the act on his Facebook page and said the tactic seemed to work at separating the two

Ms Tiefenthal said the girl's parents were also angry at the way she had been treated.

The school immediately suspended the teacher and spoke with the parents of both teens.

The bucket water incident was captured on CCTV cameras that are placed in the school's corridor.

